The '''Kabal Central Citadel''' was a centralized building in [[Shoribus]], [[Kabal/Legends|Kabal]]. It was damaged by protestors in riots after the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Galactic Republic]] increased taxation on the [[Sharlissian Trade Corridor]]. That made the route costly to travel, causing food shipments to not reach the planet.

